      • loadComponents

        public void loadComponents(java.lang.String filePath)
        This function load map components take input as filePath to a JSON file. the format of json file will include the map format as csv file. delimit end of each row as a ';'. seperate each tile as a ','. Tiles map can be creates on project website. netflot.github.io
        Parameters:
        filePath -
        Throws:
        org.json.simple.parser.ParseException
        java.io.IOException
